list.abstract: 联邦又称联邦制国家，是指由两个或两个以上的成员单位(州、省、邦、共和国等) 根据联邦宪法组成的国家。联邦是复合国中最主要的形式，世界上许多国家，如瑞士、俄罗斯、美国、加拿大、德国、印度等，都是联邦制国家。联邦国家有自己的宪法，并设立联邦立法、司法和行政机关，对联邦成员及其人民直接行使权力; 根据联邦宪法划分联邦与其成员之间的权限，联邦成员各有自己相对独立的立法、司法和行政机关，在管理内部事务方面有较大的自主权; 联邦所有成员的公民具有联邦的统一国籍; 联邦本身是统一的国际法主体，外交权一般由联邦政府统一行使，联邦成员不具有国际法主体资格。 联邦（英语：Commonwealth）是构成有机整体的政治单元，通常由原先的独立单元所组成，这些单元已将其主要权力交给整体政府，它可能是其中一个单元的政府或者是新成立的政府。该词用法接近拉丁文“条约”的意义，是一种建立在忠诚基础上的关系。

yingyinNormal.en: Impersonating a federal employee? Where's the after-party, prison?
yingyinNormal.zh: 冒充联邦雇员吗？你们的庆功宴在哪举办，监狱吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I can't park in front like this. It's a federal building!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能停在这里，这是联邦大楼。

yingyinNormal.en: We have to work together at every level, federal, state and local.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们必须在每一个层面上都精诚合作，联邦，州以及当地政府。

yingyinNormal.en: Disrespecting a federal officer. Maybe that'll get you somewhere. Who's she?
yingyinNormal.zh: 藐视国家官员，也许应该把你关起来，她是谁？

yingyinNormal.en: Unfortunately, lying on a federal form is a punishable offense. 5 years jail time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 倒霉的是，税收表格上作假是重罪，要判刑5年。

yingyinNormal.en: His name is Norman Stansfield, and he's in room 4602, in the D.E.A. Building, 26 Federal Plaza.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他叫诺曼·史丹菲尔德，他住在4602，联邦广场26号缉毒大楼4602。

yingyinNormal.en: You must know that you have the full support of the federal government here. It... Well… What's next?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你一定要知道联邦政府会全力支持你。接下来怎么办？

yingyinNormal.en: Do you know what his federal benefits covered? Not very much. That's the reason they have been calling here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道他的联邦福利有多少吗？很少一点，所以他们才一直给家里打电话。

yingyinNormal.en: Right now, a worker on the federal minimum wage earns $7.25 an hour. It's time to raise that to $10.10 an hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当下,在联邦最低工资标准下,一个员工每小时可以挣到$7.25。是时候,将其提高到每小时$10.10了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I've done what I can on my own by requiring federal contractors to pay their workers at least ten-ten an hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经做了我能做得事情，要求联邦的承包商支付给他们员工的工资最少是每小时$10.10。

yingyinNormal.en: Raising the federal minimum wage to $10.10 an hour, or ten-ten would benefit 28 million American workers. 28 million.
yingyinNormal.zh: 提高联邦最低工资标准到每小时$10.10,或者10-10，将造福于美国2800万的国人。2800万。

yingyinNormal.en: Everything being said now, everything that was just discussed, we'll have to repeat at some point to federal investigators.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在起我们所说的一切，我们刚刚讨论的一切，以后都要在联邦调查人员面前复述一遍。

yingyinNormal.en: And I've assured Governor Cuomo and Mayor de Blasio that they'll have all the federal support they need as they go forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也向科莫州长和白思豪市长保证他们将一直能够获得他们需要的所有联邦支持。

yingyinNormal.en: What I want is a stepping stone. And what you want is federal funding for a breast cancer center run by Planned Parenthood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是想要个跳板，而你想联邦资助一家计划生育组织经营的乳腺癌中心。

yingyinNormal.en: Here at the White House, my new Ebola response coordinator is working to ensure a seamless response across the federal government.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在白宫，新的埃博拉快速反应协调员正在工作，确保整个联邦政府可以做到无缝响应。

yingyinNormal.en: Enter the Federal Aviation Administration, or FAA, which maintains our complex flight-management system today. Here's how it works.
yingyinNormal.zh: 进入联邦导航系统，它包括了我们现代复杂的航空管理系统，则是它的运作方式。

yingyinNormal.en: I could come here today and talk about federal sentencing disparities between crack and cocaine, which obviously are racially motivated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我今天可以在这儿谈论大麻和可卡因的联邦量刑差异，这其中显然存在种族因素。

yingyinNormal.en: Infrastructure at the state and federal level. Increasing the size of the military, and working with our friends in the private sector to start…
yingyinNormal.zh: 州和联邦基础建设项目，扩大军队，并与私营部门合作。

yingyinNormal.en: I've tried to do my part by requiring companies that get contracts with the federal government to pay their workers a fair wage of $10.10 an hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也在尽我自己的力量要求联邦政府合同承包商为其员工提供10.10美元每小时的工资。

yingyinNormal.en: In fact, monetary policy is set by an independent Federal Reserve System, or The Fed, made up of 12 regional banks in major cities around the country.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上，货币政策是由独立的联邦准备系统制定，也就是联准会，其下有十二家区域银行散布在美国的各大都市。
